{"tid":549813,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【比特幣急跌】美銀行閂水喉 禁信用卡購虛擬貨幣","createTime":"2018-02-04T05:18:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-04T11:34:33.000Z","uid":17738,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1a3888094a0bf5bd3f857ee7bbef5ef65521a9cb","tid":549813,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T05:18:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180203/large/1517641419_cce6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180203%2Flarge%2F1517641419_cce6.jpg&h=39205253&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n比特幣（Bitcoin）從高位累挫6成，昨曾跌穿8000美元水平，摩通及美銀率先閂水喉，禁止用旗下信用卡交易任何虛擬貨幣。追蹤各類加密貨幣報價的Coinmarketcap顯示，比特幣今稍回升至8634美元水平。<br />\n<br />\n外電報導，隨著近期比特幣價格急跌，不少發卡銀行開始禁止用信用卡購買比特幣，避免因價格急跌而不能還款。此外，監管機構亦要求當地銀行慎防洗黑錢的交易，而虛擬貨幣則令監管更難。<br />\n另外，日本加密貨幣交易平台Coincheck早前失竊值5.3億美元的虛擬貨幣NEM，之後禁止客戶提取款項。Coincheck表示，已準備回復提取服務，惟無提及時間表。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180203/57788346\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180203%2F57788346&d=DnNAoCEY61nQzabBFrNAfJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=48fbd1c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180203%2F57788346&h=2eeb85f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180203/57788346</a>"},{"pid":"79fde93cbdda1e88523a40cd6b0de59eb5532698","tid":549813,"uid":72009,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T05:30:41.000Z","msg":"連登仔:bitcoin終有一天取代美元，你地即管笑"},{"pid":"3889cafe0833e609bd42452adc248dbcf1041e47","tid":549813,"uid":53429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T06:50:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  而家咪又升番囉<br />\n老貓同連登仔都睇衰既野準備升爆廠啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c58ed9e55b47ab5eb620d67917b43073cdb1e096","tid":549813,"uid":126329,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T11:34:33.000Z","msg":"連登仔：bic camera都有用bitcoin做交易<br />\n終有一日bitcoin. 會成為貨幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}